# Capacitor / native build artifacts
node_modules/
# The generated Android project — commit it if you want it versioned, otherwise
# regenerate with `npx cap add android`. Uncomment the next line to ignore it.
# android/
.gradle/
*.keystore
*.jks
# Keep the committed signing keys so neither is ever lost again — groundlink.keystore
# (debug-grade, local/sideload builds) and groundlink-upload.keystore (the real Play Store
# upload key, release builds only — has to be a separate file since Google Play rejects a
# debug-flavored certificate as an upload key):
!android/app/groundlink.keystore
!android/app/groundlink-upload.keystore
local.properties
